---
title: Invitation Lifecycle
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending: invite(group, from, to)

    Pending --> Accepted: accept(group, user)
    Pending --> Declined: decline(group, user)
    Pending --> Revoked: revoke(group, from, to)

    Accepted --> [*]
    Declined --> [*]
    Revoked --> [*]

    note right of Pending
        Invitee notified
        Awaiting response
    end note

    note right of Accepted
        Triggers: Group.addMember
        Triggers: Notification to group
    end note

    note right of Declined
        No group change
        Invitation removed
    end note

    note right of Revoked
        Inviter canceled
        Invitation removed
    end note
